                     <title xml:lang="fa" key="work_1057">حملۀ حیدری</title>
                     <note>F1a: signature of David Price. A later addition to the catalogue falsely states that this was Bagnold's copy and that Price's was a second one, called 179a by Codrington. Text incomplete at end, but not owing to the loss of folios; the MS is evidently copied from a defective one. Folio preceding text, verso: note quoting Sir William Ouseley's comments on his copy. Text includes a continuation on the life of 'Ali, not yet indentified. Headings in red.</note>
